An Kalmus (Br. über Lie-Liechens Anregung!): Auftrag;
              The official document according to which Universal Edition was to publish Free Composition. A few days later Schenker received the contract from the publishers, which he signed and returned on July 7; see the diary entries from June 23 and July 7, 1934.
              Stellungnahme zu seinem Korrekturvorbehalt – nur kein „Ueber-Nutzen“!

Von v. Hoboken (Br.): dankt für den Brief, eignet sich meine Definition seines Gutes an;
              That is, the significance of the plot of land Hoboken has acquired in Vienna, and his intention to build a villa on it.
              läßt Schmidt zu einer Konferenz nach Holland kommen, erholt sich „vom Nichtstun, das sehr ermattet.“
